QuestData.Title: Insurrection: As Strong As Our Will
QuestData.Description: In the wake of Elisande's attack, the need is stronger than ever to add to the ranks of the Nightfallen rebellion.$b$bPlans are in motion that may help with this in an unconventional way.$b$BReport to First Arcanist Thalyssra in Shal'Aran for more details.
QuestData.LogDescription: Meet with First Arcanist Thalyssra in Shal'Aran.
